Q10. When people are really happy, energized, and passionate about their talents, interests, or hobbies, we say they have a “spark” in their life.

Q10b. Which of the following are reasons that you are not more involved with your talents, interests, or hobbies?
RESPONSE FREQUENCY PERCENT VARIABLE
I dont know what my talents, interests, or hobbies are 61 29.69 q10b
I dont have enough time for them 33 14.92 q10b
I dont have enough money to pay for the equipment, supplies, lessons, etc 32 13.98 q10b
I dont know how to get more involved with them 14 8.78 q10b
I feel I cant pursue them because of my race, appearance, and or gender 8 4.92 q10b
I feel too sad or anxious to figure them out 23 12.46 q10b
I dont feel its safe to explore them 3 0.81 q10b
I dont have access to the resources to get more involved with them 8 6.17 q10b
I dont have the support from my family, friends, or community to pursue them 6 0.39 q10b
Other 10 3.27 q10b
Not sure 7 1.57 q10b
Don’t wish to answer 9 3.04 q10b
